column5: For fans of the car show "Top Gear", a couple lines from the test drive will surely get your imagination running. "I've got 120 horsepower in this; you don't want any more on marble." "Aye, look at that! The smoke grenades fit perfectly in the cup holder!"
Jeremy is the best, haven't seen that ep, great one!  And it's so convenient that smoke grenades fit in the couple holder, brilliant!  Best car show around.
Great Clip!!!! Fantastic show. Hilarious everytime!
One of my favorite episodes!  I've got every episode from all 14 seasons!
